    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>You unleash a virulent disease on a creature that you can see within range. The target must make a &amp;Reference[con]{Constitution} saving throw. On a failed save, it takes 14d6 &amp;Reference[necrotic]{necrotic} damage, or half as much damage on a successful save. The damage can't reduce the target's hit points below 1. If the target fails the saving throw, its hit point maximum is reduced for 1 hour by an amount equal to the &amp;Reference[necrotic]{necrotic} damage it took. Any effect that removes a disease allows a creature's hit point maximum to return to normal before that time passes.</p>\n</div>",
